			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1) Start TUT_Avernus_C&#xD;&#xA;2) Recruit Us by calling oe TUT_Laboratory_FreeUs in ReCon&#xD;&#xA;3) Teleport to -82; 18; -388 and interact with the transponder with Us" />
